# "Searches case insensitively if the pattern is all lowercase. Search case sensitively otherwise."
# This is really useful in the general case of doing `rg text` and wanting to match case-insensitively on "text".
--smart-case
# "Search hidden files and directories"
--hidden
# "Will force ripgrep to follow symlinks"
--follow
# "Exclude files and directories for searching that match the given glob"
--glob=!'{node_modules,.git,.DS_STORE,registry,target}'
